      • calculerResultat

        public void calculerResultat(int today,
                             java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> listNoeudRoute,
                             java.util.List<java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>> listResultatRoute,
                             java.util.List<java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>> listResultat)
        Match feasible node paths today with paths yesterday to get all feasible node paths for whole travel If the end node of yesterday is the starting node of today, like [7] then paths today [7,8,9,10] match paths yesterday [0,3,5,7], write paths combined [0,3,5,7,8,9,10] in the list of temporary results
        Parameters:
        today - The day number of today
        listNoeudRoute - Feasible node paths for each meal or each night
        listResultatRoute - A list of temporary results within all feasible node paths for whole travel
        listResultat - A list of all feasible node paths for whole travel
